snippet.title: Metroid Remix Teaser
snippet.description:
Teaser video for the upcoming metroid fangame, Metroid Remix. 

For more information about the project, visit here. http://www.metroid-remix.com/

EDIT: Demo 1 has been released. Expect more updates on the site and forums.
